Subject: Watershed (Christian band) 
To: Pamela
Content:
Watershed is an music group. Singing in the a cappella style (with the addition of Tony Brown's "beatboxing"), the group produced its first album, Audience of One in 2002. Since then, the group has produced four more albums, with their latest, I Know You Love Me being released in 2007. The ministry involved with the band is known as "Watershed Worship." Current Members are Chris Lindsey (baritone), Todd Dunaway (bass), Sean Algaier (tenor), Michael Forehand (tenor), and Tony Brown (vocal percussion). Albums with songs by year.
